summary: The mod adds a new public bathhouse to Solitude.
descriptionHtml:
People of Skyrim need a place of hygiene more than advanced knee surgery...

Features:
-1 merchant, selling potions, ingredients and wine (0-24)(+alchemy workbench)
-swimming pool
-2 hot pools
-sauna
-shower
-boiler room (+furnace)
-shower
-dressing rooms you can steel from
-4 underdressed poolside hotties (both sexes, one argonian)

Sorry, navmesh is sometimes funny. Everything is vanilla.
author: Zuzmoo
